Alexander Chuka Iwobi (/ ɪˈwoʊbi/ ih-WOH-bee; amuru 3 Mee 1996) bu onye okacha amara n’egwuregwu ndi Naijiria nke na-egwu egwu dika onye nku maka iko Premier League Everton na otu mba Naijiria.
Iwobi malitere ọrụ ya na Arsenal, na-eme ngosi 149 ma nweta ihe mgbaru ọsọ 15, wee merie FA Cup na 2017
N'August 2019, ọ gafere Everton maka ego mbụ £ 28 nde.
Iwobi nọchitere anya England ruo n'okpuru 18 larịị
O mere egwuregwu izizi ya nke mba ụwa na Nigeria na Ọktoba 2015, ma so na ndị otu ha na FIFA World Cup na 2018 na iko mba Africa na 2019 na 2021, gbachara nke atọ na asọmpi 2019.
A mụrụ Iwobi na Lagos tupu ọ kwaga England mgbe ọ dị afọ anọ , na-eso nwa oge nọrọ na Turkey   wee tolite na Newham, London
Nwanne nne ya bụbu onye egwuregwu bọọlụ bụ Jay-Jay Okocha
Iwobi sonyeere Arsenal mgbe ọ ka nọ na ụlọ akwụkwọ praịmarị, na 2004, ma ọ fọrọ nke nta ka ọ hapụ ya mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na anọ na ọzọ mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na isii.
O tinyere aka na egwuregwu otu nke mbụ dị ka onye nnọchi na-ejighị ya na Njikọ Njikọ megide West Bromwich Albion na 25 Septemba 2013
Ọ bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta ogologo oge na Arsenal na October 2015
Na 27 October 2015, Iwobi mere egwuregwu mbụ ya maka ụlọ ọrụ ahụ, malite na 3-0 meriri Sheffield Wednesday na Round nke 16 nke Njikọ Njikọ
O mere mpụta mbụ ya na Premier League ụbọchị anọ ka e mesịrị na mmeri 3-0 megide Swansea City na ama egwuregwu nnwere onwe, dị ka oge nkwụsịtụ maka Mesut Ozil
Iwobi mere mpụta mbụ Champions League ka ọ nọchiri nkeji iri asatọ na ise na mmeri 5-1 megide Bayern Munich
Iwobi malitere na otu nke mbụ maka iko FA 2015–16 nke atọ na nke anọ meriri Sunderland na Burnley n'otu n'otu

Mgbe ọ nwesịrị mmalite Njikọ Njikọ nke mbụ na mmeri 3-1 pụọ na Barcelona, Iwobi gara n'ihu nweta ihe mgbaru ọsọ abụọ na Premier League abụọ mbụ ya malitere na mmeri megide Everton, na Watford, n'otu n'otu.
Na oge na-esote, Iwobi gbanwere nọmba ndị otu ya site na 45 ruo 17, mgbe Alexis Sánchez weere nọmba 7 site na ọpụpụ Tomáš Rosický
Ọ gara n'ihu na-egosipụta oge niile Arsenal meriri iko FA nke 2016-17, merie 2-1 megide Chelsea na ikpeazụ
O nwetara ihe ịga nke ọma na Arsenal na 2017 Community Shield, nke Arsenal meriri Chelsea na ntaramahụhụ
N'ọnwa Jenụwarị afọ 2018, e wepụtara vidiyo nke eboro gosiri Iwobi na oriri abalị awa iri atọ na isii tupu egwuregwu
Na May 2018, mgbe onye njikwa Arsenal Arsène Wenger kwuputara na ọ ga-ahapụ ụlọ ọrụ ahụ, Iwobi kọwara ya dị ka "mkpali" ma kwuo na ọ dị mwute ma na-akpali akpali.
N'August 2018, ọ bịanyere aka n'akwụkwọ nkwekọrịta ogologo oge ọhụrụ na ụlọ ọrụ ahụ, a kọrọ ruo mgbe 2023
Na Jenụwarị 2019, Iwobi bụ isiokwu nke ebubo ịkpa ókè agbụrụ sitere n'aka onye na-eme ihe nkiri India Esha Gupta, onye nnọchi anya Arsenal
Na July 2019, mgbe 2019 Africa Cup of Nations, o kwuru na ya na-atụ anya ịlaghachi na football football na Arsenal
Na 8 August 2019, Iwobi bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta afọ ise na Everton
Dị ka BBC si kwuo, Arsenal nwetara ego nke mbụ £ 28 nde, na-arị elu na £ 34 nde nwere ike tinye-ons
Ụbọchị iri na ise ka ọ bịanyere aka na ya, Iwobi mere mpụta mbụ ya dị ka onye nọchiri anya ọkara elekere ikpeazụ n'ọnọdụ Gylfi Sigurðsson na mmeri 2-0 na Aston Villa
Na 28 Ọgọst na agba nke abụọ nke iko EFL, o meriri goolu Everton mbụ ya na mmeri 4–2 na Lincoln City
Ọ meriri ihe mgbaru ọsọ mbụ ya na 1 Septemba na 3-2 meriri Wolverhampton Wanderers, ma bụrụ otu n'ime ndị egwuregwu abụọ a họpụtara maka otuto site n'aka onye njikwa Marco Silva ka emechara
N'ịbụ onye ruru eru ịnọchite anya England ma ọ bụ obodo a mụrụ ya Nigeria, Iwobi malitere dị ka onye ntorobịa mba ụwa maka England, onye ya na ya meriri 2011 Victory Shield
Iwobi nwetara ọkpụ iri na otu n'England n'ọkwa na-erubeghị afọ, mana ọ gara n'ihu kwupụtaara Naịjirịa n'afọ 2015
O mere egwuregwu mbụ ya maka Super Eagles na 8 October, dochie Ahmed Musa na nkeji 57th nke 2-0 enyi na enyi meriri DR Congo na Visé, Belgium
Naijiria họpụtara ya maka ndị otu ha dị mmadụ iri atọ na ise maka asọmpi Olimpiks Summer 2016
Ọ soghị na ndị egwuregwu 18 ikpeazụ
N'August 2017 Iwobi chụpụrụ n'otu Nigeria maka asọmpi Iko Mbaụwa nke ọnwa ahụ n'ihi mmerụ ahụ
N'October 2017, Iwobi meriri Nigeria na 1-0 meriri Zambia iji nweta Super Eagles otu ebe na 2018 FIFA World Cup na Russia
Akpọrọ ya aha n'ime ndị mmadụ iri abụọ na atọ na Naịjirịa maka asọmpi a wee sonye n'egwuregwu atọ a ka agbapụrụ Super Eagles n'ọkwa otu.
N'August 2017 Iwobi chụpụrụ n'otu Nigeria maka asọmpi Iko Mbaụwa nke ọnwa ahụ n'ihi mmerụ ahụ
N'October 2017, Iwobi meriri Nigeria na 1-0 meriri Zambia iji nweta Super Eagles otu ebe na 2018 FIFA World Cup na Russia
Akpọrọ ya aha n'ime ndị mmadụ iri abụọ na atọ na Naịjirịa maka asọmpi a wee sonye n'egwuregwu atọ a ka agbapụrụ Super Eagles n'ọkwa otu.
Akpọrọ Iwobi n'otu egwuregwu Naịjirịa maka asọmpi iko mba Afrịka nke afọ 2021 na-egbu oge n'afọ 2022
E nyere ya kaadị uhie nkeji ise ka ọ nọchiri ya na asọmpi knockout ha na Tunisia, egwuregwu Nigeria meriri 0-1.
